      "ko_pron": "Ijeneun naega geudae jikil teni",
      "time": "00:00:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Your embrace was always warm",
      "zh": "你的懷抱總是溫暖",
      "ja": "너의 품은 항상 따뜻했어",
